  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility Notes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Include fallback text</strong>: Content between tags is shown if progress is not supported</li>
      <li><strong>Use labels</strong>: Always associate a label with the progress element</li>
      <li><strong>Announce updates</strong>: Consider using <code>aria-live</code> for important progress updates</li>
      <li><strong>Provide context</strong>: Include percentage or step numbers in visible text</li>
      <li><strong>Screen reader support</strong>: Progress elements are announced as "X% complete"</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

